return {title = "Spirit Shackles", id = 674, description = {'After this effect occurs, it cannot activate again until Isaac gains a half or full Soul Heart or a Black Heart. Soul Hearts that are used to charge Spirit Shackles will not be added to your health as normal', "When you die, you turn into a ghost with 1/2 a red heart and flying, that is chained to your body for 10 seconds. This allows you to stay alive as long as you don't get hit during this 10 second period"}}